member.name: T:ISNet.WebUI.WebDesktop.WebToolBar
member.summary: Intersoft WebToolBar.NET WebControl for ASP.NET.
member.remarks:
The WebToolBar.NET control is used to display toolbar menu at ASP.NET environment. The WebToolBar.NET control supports following features :
Docking capabilities when it is layouted on the PlaceHolderManager.Customize window feature when it is layouted on the PlaceHolderManager.WebToolBar standalone capabilities when it is layouted on the Page.WebToolBar merging to another page at another frame window.WebToolBar style : Office2003, Office2000, OfficeXP, IE, and ComplexImages.WebToolBar fully customizable styles at handle region, body region and option region.Tool command more items capabilities (showing and hiding tool commands).Tool command moving, ordering, showing, hiding capabilities when it is layouted on PlaceHolderManager.Tool command enabling capabilities (enabling and disabling tool commands).Tool command type : Button, ToggleButton, DropDownButton, SplitButton, Separator, Custom, and Container.Tool command grouping for toggle button.Tool command merging to another webtoolbar at another frame window.Tool command client side events.
